<div style="font-family: Arial; font-size:15px;">

<table width="90%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1" align="center" bgcolor="#333333"><tr><td>
<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="16" align="center" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
  <tr><td align="right"><%= @distributor.name %></td></tr>
  <tr><td>

<strong>Thanks for your order <%= @customer.first_name %>!</strong><br>
<br>

Did you know you can view and edit your orders 24 hours a day? Visit <%= link_to "your account", new_customer_session_url(distributor: @distributor.parameter_name) %><br>
<br>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0" border="1" bordercolor="#555555">
    <tr>
        <td bgcolor="#555555">
            <font color="#FFFFFF" size="+1">
                <b>Order Information:</b>
            </font>
        </td>
    </tr>

    <tr>
      <td>
      <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="8" width="100%">
        <tr>
        <td width="50%" valign="top">
          <span style="font-size:14px">
          <b>Customer Number:</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;<%= @customer.formated_number %><br>
          <b>E-mail:</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;<%= @customer.email %><br>
          <b>Phone:</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;<%= @customer.address.default_phone_number %><br>
          </span>
        </td>

        <td width="50%" valign="top">
          <span style="font-size:14px">
          <b>Delivery Address:</b><br>
          <%= @customer.name %>
          <br/>
          <%= @customer.address.to_s("<br/>") %>
          </span>
        </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
    </tr>
</table>

<br>
<br>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0" border="1" bordercolor="#555555">
    <tr>
        <td bgcolor="#555555" size="+1" colspan="2">
            <font color="#FFFFFF">
                <b>Order Summary:</b>
          </font>
        </td>
    </tr>

  <tr>
  <td width="80%" valign="top">
    <b><%= @order.box.name %></b><br>
    <span style="font-size:14px">
    Exclude: <%= @order.exclusions_string %><br>
    Substitute: <%= @order.substitutions_string %><br>
    <%= Order.extras_description(@order.order_extras) %>
    <br>
    <i><%= @order.schedule_rule %></i><br>
    </span>
  </td>
  </td>

  <td width="20%" align="right" valign="top">
    <b><%= @order.price %></b><br/>
  </td>
  </tr>

</table>


<br>
<br>

You can review your orders and your account statement at anytime by logging into <%= link_to "your account", new_customer_session_url(distributor: @distributor.parameter_name) %>.<br>
<br>
If you have any questions or feel something is out of place, please get in touch at <%= @distributor.support_email %><%= " or #{@distributor.phone}" if @distributor.phone.present? %>.


</td></tr></table>
</td></tr></table>

</div>

